<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8390451>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Photographs of male (A–D) and female (E, F, G, H) of Callitrichia protegularis n. sp., paratypes from Eth008. A, E, habitus, dorsal view; B, prosoma, dorsal view; C, same, lateral view; D, habitus frontal view; F, opisthosoma, ventral view; G, H, epigynum and cleared epigynum, respectively, ventral view. Scale bars: A–F, 0.5mm; G, H, 0.1mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8390451/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8390453>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Details of male palpal structure (A–E) and female epigynum (F) of Callitrichia protegularis n. sp., paratypes from Eth008. A, B, right palp, retrolateral and prolateral view, respectively; C, tibia and paracymbium, prolateral view; D, same, dorsal view; E, embolic division, prolateral view; F, cleared epigynum, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.1mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8390453/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8390443>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Photographs of male (A, B, C, D) and female (E, F, G) of Callitrichia asela n. sp., paratypes from Eth017. A, E, habitus, dorsal view; B, same, lateral view; C, prosoma, antero-lateral view; D, F, habitus frontal view; G, opisthosoma, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.5mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8390443/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

